{"tid":546794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[右傾連登仔]研究指外貌較佳者 政治立場偏向右傾","createTime":"2018-01-31T23:41:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-01T01:48:59.000Z","uid":132859,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e12f5ddadd70318c0d79dc330bc7f6967551e309","tid":546794,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T23:41:14.000Z","msg":"你的樣子如何，政治立場也必如何？美國有研究指，外貌較佳者的政治立場偏向右傾，反之外貌欠佳者偏向左傾，因為前者在日常生活中受到較佳待遇，繼而較少同情他人的不幸。<br />\n<br />\n絕大部份人都認為自己的政見是基於客觀分析論點後而定，惟美國伊利諾州立大學政治系助理教授帕爾默（Carl Palmer）、薩斯奎漢納大學政治科學系助理教授彼得森（Rolfe Daus Peterson）指，人的外觀亦能對人生和政見產生巨大影響。<br />\n<br />\n兩人研究1970年代的美國政治民調和威斯康辛州一個由高中開始追蹤60年調查數據，兩研究除紀錄政治立場、性別等資料，亦有受訪者外貌評分，「發現外貌較佳者有較高水平的政治效能感，亦通常是保守派和共和黨」。高政治效能感是指民眾能理解政治事務和相信自己有能力影響政局。<br />\n<br />\n過往多份研究指出外貌能顯著影響人們的生活經驗。彼得森舉例指，外觀較佳的兒童會得到父母和他人的較貼心待遇，長大後變得更有自信、善於社交、樂觀等，「當我們受到不同待遇，所理解的世界亦會有所差異」，對他人的困境產生「盲點」，令政見或多或少右傾。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180131&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=57777547\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180131%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D57777547&d=zEBK3YvARoZsHEwA%2BxTlJcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=675fa3d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180131%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D57777547&h=cdcfcc77\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180131&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=57777547</a><br />\n咁連登一定好多(鬼佬眼中)既靚仔靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7993d5963ddb12c7fa7d36f0c6a0f68896fc7c76","tid":546794,"uid":35014,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T23:46:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"32b2b95ba43f9bb8e4c09154a1b6c512bfedc1d9","tid":546794,"uid":90863,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"7993d5963ddb12c7fa7d36f0c6a0f68896fc7c76","tid":546794,"uid":35014,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T23:46:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T23:53:14.000Z","msg":"研究咁辛苦就咁比張圖收左皮"},{"pid":"1c3111590bc8568b88bea0350f3e671f391c0512","tid":546794,"uid":71725,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T00:19:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"641cd770d2d8ef20dc3828d1e62bd91d80993222","tid":546794,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1c3111590bc8568b88bea0350f3e671f391c0512","tid":546794,"uid":71725,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T00:19:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T00:30:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五毛侵B</span>"},{"pid":"39429ec58deb10a9710048fb4435b18fdb1d8a22","tid":546794,"uid":47359,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"641cd770d2d8ef20dc3828d1e62bd91d80993222","tid":546794,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1c3111590bc8568b88bea0350f3e671f391c0512","tid":546794,"uid":71725,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T00:19:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T00:30:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五毛侵B</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T00:31:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/01/083131_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F01%2F083131_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=2ab603ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3f3e8f2745b9cfe9b8dd399f249f81f5deb4fcfc","tid":546794,"uid":17859,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T00:33:29.000Z","msg":"人哋講得隱晦啲啫<br />\n咁咪即係班左賊生得零舍樣衰<br />\n狗閪咁嘅款囉"},{"pid":"8fed46a17d1db839bf0342734cc9a4668fbad108","tid":546794,"uid":59898,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T00:34:36.000Z","msg":"啱呀，你睇下民國復興條撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lo